      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a sophisticated balance of performance and reliability. This specimen has been curated to ensure mechanical excellence and aesthetic consistency, featuring a clean interior profile and a powertrain that remains responsive and robust. Ideal for the discerning driver, this motorcar represents a secure investment in long-term utility and refined road presence. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate its distinguished condition firsthand.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
